Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:35.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手を伸ばして　焦がれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.60,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}届くはずない　光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.56,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こんな世界で　こんな世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.15,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}何度も見てた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:57.74,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}君の割れた　硝子細工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.46,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}触れた指が　痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:05.71,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}大切なもの　要らないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.53,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}元には戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.39,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　一雫　頬を濡らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:16.31,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}切なく　雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}まだ何も君を知らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.77,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}その涙が　止まったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.57,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}笑ってみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.91,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あ憧れて　憧れて　想像を形へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.77,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}変えるリアリティ　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:42.05,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行くよ　窓の外は君を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.96,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.52,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:51.10,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:57.72,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.85,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
Comment: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:32.48,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,OP-CN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:35.52,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我所伸出的手　如此急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.60,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所無法傳達　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.56,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地裡　在這樣的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:46.15,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若夢　回眸幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:57.74,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所製作的　玻璃飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.46,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一觸　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:05.71,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:08.53,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至終　覆水難收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:13.39,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　僅需一滴　臉頰便能浸潤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:16.31,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀絞　雨恨雲愁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.72,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我還是對你　一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:25.77,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落淚　就此止泣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.57,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想與你　歡聲笑語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.91,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此嚮往　想像便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.77,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改變當下　於晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:42.05,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出發吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:43.96,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}攜手與你共賞春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:46.52,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑雲已散　風光日霽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:51.10,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨後鏡花水月　依舊彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:57.72,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨過天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.85,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不過我想讓你　所尋自己而已
